captions.text: "The Clucking Bumblehound"

Oh I couldn't eat another bite.
I'm going to go read a magazine.

Yeah go read a magazine! I'm
sure you'll find something

real interesting. And in the
meantime I'll eat your cake

Since you can't eat another bite of
this, is it OK if I give it to my guys?
Go for it!
Wait! I have something to tell you!!
What??
Someone really wants that cake!
Who?
Duh! I uhhh...
The Clucking Bumblehound!
The Clucking Bumblehound?? What's that??

Ohhh, it lives in the hills.
It's big and terrifying!

It moves very very fast, so
fast that nobody can see it!

It loves anything sweet, and
it, it gathers nectar like

a bee does. But from food. Like cookies.
And that cake.
Wowsy-powsy!!

Nobody's actually laid eyes on the
horrible beast, but they know that he

comes, in the middle of the night to
take your treats back home with him.

Maybe we should leave this
piece of cake out tonight,

then, the Chicken Bee, I
mean the Bumble Dog...

Why not? That's not a bad idea.
It's best to know exactly

how much danger we're in. We'll
just leave it right here.

I wanna hear everything there is to
know about the Buzzing Chickenhound.

Well, from what I've heard he's like a giant
yellow jacket with a big chicken's beak.

And he's completely covered
in fur like a wild wolf hound

He's got long fangs, and he
buzzes when he flies around

And another thing he does? He makes
weird chicken sounds, like this!!
Is this him?
Well I guess it's uh, that's it time for bed!

Guess what I'm doing! I'm staying
up to wait for him! I'm gonna

hide right over here, like this,
and wait for him to come in!

I'll get a picture of him
when he goes to eat the cake!
That's never going to work!
Why?

You can't look at him because he's so
terrifying that you'll run away screaming!

Then your throat will hurt so bad, you
won't be able to talk for a whole week!

Now Kid, it's time for bed baby brother!
Let's just set this aside right over here.

When you wake up in the
morning we'll see if the

Clucking Bumblehound has
been here or if he hasn't.

Does the Clucking Bumblehound like
to eat anything besides sweet stuff?

Oh I don't know let me think about it!
What else does he like??

Here, here you go!!! He
likes salt, and he likes

garlic, and he really
really likes pepper, OK????
Now please go to bed!!!

What are you screaming about?? Did he come??
Did you see the bumblehound???

I knew it would work!! You see?! I
used all of the things he likes best!

I took lots of salt and a piece of garlic and a
ton of pepper and I put it all inside that cake!

But it didn't even matter,
cause you scared him away.
Hold on a minute!!!

Mommy told me not to tell
anybody about this, but

she likes to keep an extra
package of cake up here.

She said they're just for
special occasions, but it's

not every day that a terrifying
monster comes to visit.

I don't know, I don't think the
Clucking Bumblehound will mind

if we just eat a couple as
long as we leave some for him.
